1
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:05,840
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,260 --> 00:01:09,890
[Episode 9]

3
00:01:22,230 --> 00:01:23,200
How is he?

4
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,710
Can I go in now?

5
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,789
Not yet.

6
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:28,400
His Majesty won't even cooperate
with the royal physician,

7
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,430
let alone allow anyone near him.

8
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,760
He drifts in and out

9
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:32,820
of consciousness.

10
00:01:33,789 --> 00:01:34,990
If this continues...

11
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,000
Miss Jiang,

12
00:01:36,789 --> 00:01:39,310
I'm afraid there's nothing
you can do even if you go in.

13
00:01:39,310 --> 00:01:40,200
Right now,

14
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:42,509
His Majesty would least want you to see

15
00:01:42,509 --> 00:01:43,840
his current condition.

16
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,759
Get out!

17
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:55,830
All of you, get out!

18
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:56,920
Get out!

19
00:02:00,430 --> 00:02:02,120
I said get out.

20
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,350
Did you not hear me?

21
00:02:03,350 --> 00:02:04,120
Out!

22
00:02:07,790 --> 00:02:09,710
You refuse to let
the royal physician treat you.

23
00:02:09,710 --> 00:02:11,770
Are you going to get yourself killed?

24
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:17,750
Li.

25
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,430
If you don't get treatment, you'll die.

26
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:38,960
Right now in the palace

27
00:02:39,590 --> 00:02:42,240
there are so many eyes watching me.

28
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,970
If my injuries become known,

29
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:49,310
it will only give
my enemies an opportunity.

30
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:50,240
So?

31
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,680
So...

32
00:02:53,410 --> 00:02:56,170
So you don't need to stay
in the palace anymore.

33
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,030
You should leave.

34
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,240
I'm not leaving!

35
00:03:02,190 --> 00:03:04,910
Didn't you hear me?

36
00:03:04,910 --> 00:03:06,030
I'm ordering you to leave.

37
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,400
Leave now!

38
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,520
Leave!

39
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,080
Xie Jiuzhao,

40
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,640
listen to me carefully.

41
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,840
I am not

42
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,240
someone you can
summon and dismiss at will.

43
00:03:16,079 --> 00:03:19,120
Now you'd better behave yourself!

44
00:04:00,190 --> 00:04:02,400
Whenever you see
this jade pendant from now on,

45
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:05,120
remember it means someone in this world
is still protecting you

46
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,470
and looking out for you.

47
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:59,430
Get some rest, Your Majesty.

48
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:42,740
[Ciyuan Palace]

49
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:44,830
Your Majesty!

50
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:47,120
Your Majesty!

51
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,950
Your Majesty!

52
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:49,880
Something terrible has happened!

53
00:05:50,159 --> 00:05:51,420
What's all this panic?

54
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,720
Compose yourself.

55
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,950
Ge-General Xun...

56
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:57,510
What has he done now?

57
00:05:57,510 --> 00:05:59,830
He... He led his guards
to storm the palace.

58
00:05:59,830 --> 00:06:02,960
Got captured by His Majesty
and thrown into the dungeon.

59
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,800
And His Majesty?

60
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,390
How is he?

61
00:06:10,720 --> 00:06:13,510
His Majesty forbids anyone
to approach his chambers.

62
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:15,800
There's no news at all right now.

63
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,630
I'll see to it at once.

64
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,340
Miss Jiang.

65
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,570
Here are all the materials you requested.

66
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,980
But what are you doing?

67
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,920
I'm preparing some medicine
to improve blood circulation for him.

68
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,190
Some for oral use,

69
00:06:50,390 --> 00:06:52,070
and some to apply on the wound

70
00:06:52,070 --> 00:06:53,270
so it can heal faster.

71
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,600
I'm just curious,

72
00:06:57,070 --> 00:06:58,480
how do you know all this?

73
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,190
You're worried about my skills,
aren't you?

74
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,190
Don't worry.

75
00:07:03,450 --> 00:07:05,750
My mother traveled widely in her lifetime

76
00:07:05,750 --> 00:07:08,240
and learned skills
from many talented people.

77
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:10,510
She taught me this medical skill.

78
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,870
Miss Jiang.

79
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,430
Thank you.

80
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:26,870
He was injured because of me.

81
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:29,830
How could I just stand by and do nothing?

82
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,310
Then please

83
00:07:39,430 --> 00:07:41,159
allow me to say a few more words.

84
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:43,630
His Majesty...

85
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:46,600
actually has many constraints.

86
00:07:46,950 --> 00:07:48,870
There are many things he cannot say

87
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:49,930
and many things...

88
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,000
he cannot do.

89
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:00,310
I know.

90
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:07,430
The Empress Dowager arrives!

91
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,210
-Greetings.
-Greetings.

92
00:08:26,210 --> 00:08:27,380
Your Majesty.

93
00:08:32,909 --> 00:08:34,030
Where's His Majesty?

94
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,120
Your Majesty,

95
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,600
His Majesty is resting.

96
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:38,080
Please withdraw,

97
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,220
to avoid disturbing His Majesty.

98
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,390
You dare block my way?

99
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:44,000
Commander Yuwen,

100
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,600
know your place!

101
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,750
Please allow me.

102
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,750
His Majesty is resting.

103
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,150
Your Majesty, please...

104
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,720
You're from the Jiang family.

105
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:58,150
I haven't had the chance
to punish you yet,

106
00:08:58,630 --> 00:08:59,750
and here you are,

107
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:03,000
showing no shame at all.

108
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,840
Do you know?

109
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:06,470
Your mere presence here

110
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,550
is enough for me

111
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:10,390
to sentence you to death!

112
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:15,440
If Your Majesty sentence me to death,

113
00:09:15,660 --> 00:09:17,140
I have no defense.

114
00:09:17,510 --> 00:09:19,870
But His Majesty is feeling unwell today.

115
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:23,750
Please choose another day to visit.

116
00:09:25,670 --> 00:09:28,530
There was such a commotion
in the palace last night.

117
00:09:29,120 --> 00:09:30,720
As his mother,

118
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:31,870
today

119
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,870
I must see that His Majesty
is safe and sound.

120
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,150
If you dare obstruct me further,

121
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:39,840
it'll be taken as intentionally
concealing His Majesty's condition.

122
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,770
For such a crime,

123
00:09:40,870 --> 00:09:42,800
your entire clan will be executed!

124
00:09:43,030 --> 00:09:44,630
What a lively scene

125
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:46,030
early in the morning.

126
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:06,120
Greetings, Mother.
